File Sharing - Inshare fails to meet the standards expected of a reliable file sharing app. Its sluggish transfer speeds, frequent connection issues, intrusive advertisements, lackluster user interface, and privacy concerns make it a frustrating choice for users. With numerous alternative apps available in the market offering superior performance and better user experiences, it is advisable to explore other options instead of settling for Inshare.
